{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t17-train-1","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"代数式","title":"针对训练1：求代数式的值","difficulty":3,"tags":["代数式","求值"],"content":"如果 $|x + 1| = 3$，$|y| = 5$，$-\\frac{x}{y} > 0$，那么\n\n当 $x =$ ______ 的值是\n\nA. 2 或 3\nB. -2 或 0\nC. -1 或 3\nD. 9 或 -7","steps":[{"title":"解绝对值方程","content":"$|x + 1| = 3 \\Rightarrow x + 1 = 3$ 或 $x + 1 = -3$\n\n$x = 2$ 或 $x = -4$\n\n$|y| = 5 \\Rightarrow y = 5$ 或 $y = -5$","formula":""},{"title":"分析条件","content":"$-\\frac{x}{y} > 0$ 说明 $\\frac{x}{y} < 0$，即 $x$ 与 $y$ 异号\n\n若 $x = 2 > 0$，则 $y = -5$\n若 $x = -4 < 0$，则 $y = 5$","formula":"\\text{答案：D}"}]},"id":"t17-train-1"},"__N_SSG":true}